<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-12 14:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4864 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ARTS-CHOICES-BOS &LR;      04-12 1463
