<DOCNO> NYT19990412.0310 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-12 18:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5291 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPOT-BUDGET-BOS &LR;      04-12 0452
</HEADER>
