<P>
   FIREMAIN _ ATLANTA _ Residents of this city were glued to their
television sets to watch the Monday's afternoon dramatic rescue by
helicopter of a construction worker stranded atop his crane as the
development he was working on was engulfed in flames. The fire was
so fierce that the crane's gondola caught fire and homes several
blocks away were set ablaze. (Atlanta Journal-Constitution) .
