   PIZZA-HEALTH (Los Angeles) _ Pizza with beer and wine are more
than the perfect meal: They can fight cancer and uclers, two
studies reported Monday say. One study provides the first direct
evidence that the nutrient that makes tomatoes red may protect men
against prostate cancer. Another study says beer and wine, in
addition to warding off heart attacks and cancer, could protect the
