<SLUG> BC-CONGRESS-KOSOVO-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
KOSOVO NOT HIGH ON CONGRESS' AGENDA 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (w and i coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By MICHAEL KRANISH  
 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Nearly three weeks after NATO bombing of Yugoslavia
