   BKN-ROCKETS (Minneapolis) _ Coming off another demoralizing loss
to the Utah Jazz, the Houston Rockets face another tough task
tonight against a young, energetic Minnesota Timberwolves team. By
JONATHAN FEIGEN.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-ASTROS (San Francisco) _ With their offense in a major funk
and their pitching erratic, the Houston Astros head out for their
first road trip of the season to take on a San Francisco Giants
team that is off to its hottest start in 26 years. A preview of the
three-game West Coast series. By JOSEPH DUARTE.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-DRAFT (Houston) _ Preview of the NFL Draft, focusing on the
wide receivers. By JOHN McCLAIN.
</P>
