ORGANS-AZ (Phoenix) - A bill going through the Arizona Legislature
would require all Arizona organs to remain in Arizona. It's
considered a pre-emptive strike against the Clinton
administration's plan to donate organs to those who need them the
most. The bill is setting off a battle among doctors, ethicists and
