   (NYT23) LOS ALAMOS, N.M. -- April 12, 1999 -- CHINA-NUKELAB,
4-12 -- Sens. Bob Kerrey, D-Neb., left, and Richard C. Shelby,
R-Ala., speaking at Los Alamos National Laboratory on Monday.
Denouncing the ``hemorrhaging'' of bomb secrets to foreigners,
Shelby says ``I would put a tourniquet on it.'' (Steve Northup/New
York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT22) NAZARETH, Israel -- April 12, 1999 -- NAZARETH-PLAZA-2,
4-12 -- Three Christian Arab bridesmaids headed to the Basilica of
the Annunciation in Nazareth. A bitter dispute over the site has
brought violence to Nazareth, which had been free of the tensions
roiling the Middle East. (Rina Castelnuovo/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT21) NEW YORK -- April 12, 1999 -- SOS-FASHION, 4-12 -- From
