   (NYT19) ON THE GRAND TRUNK ROAD, India -- April 12, 1999 --
PAKISTAN-BUS-2, 4-12 -- On a bus running between New Delhi, India,
and Lahore, Pakistan, an icon of peace hopes, Shezad, 5, takes in
the scenery. The bus links two countries that have fought three
wars since 1947 and whose people have been largely cut off from
each other for the decades since, with only trickles allowed to
travel into each other's territory. (Celia W. Dugger/New York Times
Photo) *LITE
