4-12 -- Dr. Linda Bartoshuk, a psychologist specializing in taste,
recently set up a video camera in her Yale University laboratory,
where she videotapes tongues in tracking down phantom tastes like
burning mouth syndrome. Dr. Bartoshuk and her colleagues will
present some of their work at the annual meeting of the Association
for Chemoreception Sciences in Sarasota, Fla., this week. (George
Ruhe/New York Times Photo) *LITE
