-- Bill Steinhour paid $5,800 for this 1987 Mercedes 300 turbo
diesel on the Internet. While retailers continue to spend furiously
to draw more customers online, the Internet is suddenly teeming
with buyers and sellers making their own markets. (Ann Grillo/New
York Times Photo)
