<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Big Entertainment, CBS make `robust' promotion deal
 &HT;    (EDS: Moving to (f) Financial and (E) Entertainment categories.)
 &HT;    By Stephen Pounds
