   10 Martin Brodeur Devils 1996-97
</P>
<P>
   10 Martin Brodeur Devils 1997-98
</P>
<P>
   10 Byron Dafoe Bruins 1998-99
</P>
<P>
   HIGH-PERCENTAGE PLAYERS
</P>
<P>
   The Mighty Ducks have two of the five players who have been
involved in the highest percentage of their team's goals, either by
scoring goals or assisting. Pittsburgh's Jaromir Jagr, the NHL's
runaway scoring leader, leads in this statistical category, but
Teemu Selanne and Paul Kariya are close behind:
</P>
